AUDIO: 'Every builder wants powerful AI in their app without cues, GPU bills, or weeks of setup. But today, you either pay premium prices or fight with complex infrastructure just to run images, voice, or video analysis at scale. Meet DAPI, one simple API that lets you run'

[00:15] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'AI instantly on a global GPU cloud without setup and limits. Generate images and videos, turn text into natural speech, transcribe fulllength videos, and swap models on the fly. All through one unified endpoint and a clean'

[00:29] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'developer UX. Because DAPI runs on a distributed GPU cloud, your inference can be up to 20 times cheaper than typical providers. Scale when you need, pay as you go. Under the hood, requests are routed across thousands of real GPUs'

[00:42] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'worldwide. The network picks the right node, runs the job, and returns your result. You never touch the infra. Lower cost, instant scale, one clear API. You build features, we run the models. Start'

[00:54] [scene:talk]
